| format = PDF
| issn = 0208-189X
| accessdate = 2007-06-02}} 
</ref>

To increase efficiency when retorting oil shale, researchers have proposed and tested several co-pyrolysis processes.<ref name=co-pyrolisis>
{{Cite journal
 | title =Co-pyrolysis of waste plastics with oil shale
 | last = Tiikma | first=Laine
